{"tid":2309169,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡英文：民主的台灣，一定會繼續相挺港人，相挺民主","createTime":"2020-12-02T11:05:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T11:25:55.000Z","uid":57205,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"76e4a660bba572f151d7ad64973ff7813426a4b4","tid":2309169,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:05:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/46251501064/posts/10157154467551065/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F46251501064%2Fposts%2F10157154467551065%2F&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOZS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=67a3945e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/46251501064/posts/10157154467551065/</a><br />\n今天香港傳來消息，「香港眾志」前秘書長 黃之鋒 Joshua Wong、前主席林朗彥、以及前成員 周庭 Agnes Chow Ting 因為去年的抗爭，遭到判刑。<br />\n　　<br />\n這三位香港的年輕人，代表了香港人民爭取民主的集體意志。非常遺憾，這個判決讓港人的民主訴求，再一次被威權所壓制。<br />\n　　<br />\n台灣也曾經在民主路上奮鬥過，我們沒有因為恐懼，就忘了心目中理想的台灣。黑夜總會過，黎明必會來，盼望香港朋友不要因為恐懼而忘記心中的理想。現在還不是絕望的時候，民主的台灣，一定會繼續相挺港人，相挺民主。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3f5U0Co.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3f5U0Co.jpg&h=2f5befab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e667a16e1ef05e8e035fd4682e0c95b60e417a0","tid":2309169,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:09:12.000Z","msg":"感謝蔡總統 照顧在台手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90310baad7408946b47ef7c07a022af8b9a95e5","tid":2309169,"uid":281713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:23:51.000Z","msg":"#StandWithHK<br />\n#AgnesChow<br />\n<br />\nTwitter 做野<br />\n<br />\n周庭黃之鋒林朗彥被極權法庭囚禁 twitter戰線整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2308914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2308914</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a1bf2a837ea2961475fbaaf6bbdc0d968a2567d9","tid":2309169,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T11:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass